s/regex_detection_skills.py (unexported skill classes)", "Confirm all 14 exported __all__ symbols in backend/skills/__init__.py are documented and that the 9+ unexported regex skills are correctly flagged as absent from the registry", "Check that LLMClient retry/backoff logic, Gemini API parameters, and error handling paths in backend/common/llm_client.py are captured with depth (not just NAME_ONLY)", "Verify PaperAuditor 4-phase pipeline and SotaAnalyzer 5-step pipeline are described with sequencing, data flow, and inter-phase dependencies", "Validate Streamlit UI coverage: session_state keys, upload flow, audit results rendering, chatbot interaction, gauge chart thresholds, and SOTA section triggers (extracted_frontend_01.md)", "Check scoring.py CHECKLIST_KEYS (16 items) and CHECKLIST_LABELS are fully enumerated with correct labels", "Confirm GAP markers are legitimately used (not used to hide known content) by cross-checking against source files"], "output_file": "review_reviewer_backend_frontend_01.md", "engine": "cli", "skills": ["re-generic", "re-review-quality"], "scope": "Quality review of extractions for the backend infrastructure (common config, LLM client, prompts, core services, utils), the backend skills subsystem (base skill, auditor/chatbot/SOTA/RAG/regex skills, skill registry), and the Streamlit frontend (app entry, UI components, styles, scoring, session state). Spot-check 15-25% of source files per cluster, prioritising files cited as evidence, the largest files (prompts.py, regex_detection_skills.py, audit_results.py), and any files carrying GAP markers."}, {"id": "reviewer_root_tests_scratch_01", "clusters_to_review": ["cluster_root_tests_scratch_01"], "load": {"files": 21, "loc": 1342, "clusters": 1}, "verification_focus": ["Verify root app.py (89 LOC) is documented with its Streamlit page config, upload flow, and audit result orchestration — confirm it is distinct from frontend/app.py coverage", "Spot-check md_to_pdf.py (325 LOC) and pdf_to_md